	(1274,2,'alejandra_0_alejandra_description','[:en]Alejandra was born in Nicaragua, educated in the United States and has lived in Paris for 20 years. A truly global citizen, she speaks five languages, has an elegant sense of style and an amazing attention to detail that allows her and her team to imagine and execute majestic events in close collaboration with their clients. She’s high energy with high expectations and will use her experience, creativity and passion to work with you to create your perfect event. [:fr]A la tête d\'une entreprise fleurissante, cette native du Nicaragua est tombée sous le charme de Paris (et de ses parisiens !), il y a bientôt plus de vingt ans. C\'est au coeur de notre capitale qu\'elle a également décelé tout le potentiel pour créer sa propre agence d\'événementiel.\r\n[:]'),
	(1275,2,'_alejandra_0_alejandra_description','field_56db13359ff37'),
	(1276,2,'alejandra_1_alejandra_image','443'),
	(1277,2,'_alejandra_1_alejandra_image','field_56db13149ff36'),
	(1278,2,'alejandra_1_alejandra_description','[:en]Alejandra, an international planner, producer and designer, has carefully crafted a brand that is cutting-edge, innovative and non-traditional. Armed with a keen eye, great enthusiasm and a willingness to break the rules, she’s able to create jaw-dropping experiences.  Her company is based in Paris but her experience and approach are global.[:fr]Alejandra se distingue par une richesse culturelle internationale et par un goût prononcé pour l\'Art, domaine dans lequel elle a d\'ailleurs travaillé de nombreuses années. Son inspiration est nourrie par ses voyages, ses découvertes culinaires, ses rencontres artistiques... une sensibilité pour le Beau et une curiosité exacerbée qui se ressentent dans chacune de ses réalisations.[:]'),
	(1279,2,'_alejandra_1_alejandra_description','field_56db13359ff37'),
	(1280,2,'alejandra_2_alejandra_image','205'),
	(1281,2,'_alejandra_2_alejandra_image','field_56db13149ff36'),
	(1282,2,'alejandra_2_alejandra_description','[:en]Alejandra’s commitment to her clients knows no bounds; she gives 110% all the time. For every location she discovers, there comes new inspiration and perspective. It is her keen curiosity about the world and how aesthetic, cultures and hospitality intertwine that make all her events something to talk about.[:fr]Folies des grandeurs à la mesure de son imagination, raffinement à la Française, esprit avant-gardiste très audacieux, Alejandra et son enthousiasme contagieux donneront vie à vos rêves le temps d’un événement d’exception, dans une ambiance grand luxe et une atmosphère feutrée.\r\n[:]'),
