	(9151,401,'_testimonials_1_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(9152,401,'testimonials_1_testimonial_content','Je voulais célébrer l\'arrivée de mon premier garçon à l\'américaine, et avec les conseils d\'une amie nous avons fait appel à Alejandra pour organiser notre « baby-shower ». Alejandra a apporté la touche personnelle en organisant la fête avec le thème très originale Ralph Lauren ! Une décoration magnifique avec un kit de maquillage bleu ciel personnalisé comme cadeau pour chaque invitée, c\'était chic. Avec Alejandra, la bonne ambiance est garantie ! J’ai hâte d’avoir une fille pour voir quelle surprise Alejandra me réserve !'),
	(9153,401,'_testimonials_1_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(9154,401,'testimonials_1_testimonial_name','Constance Hauteville (France)'),
	(9155,401,'_testimonials_1_testimonial_name','field_56e2c581ae172'),
	(9156,401,'testimonials_1_event_category','1'),
	(9157,401,'_testimonials_1_event_category','field_570d46e5dfd99'),
	(9158,401,'testimonials_2_testimonial_image','399'),
	(9159,401,'_testimonials_2_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(9160,401,'testimonials_2_testimonial_content',' Alejandra, I truly want to thank you for organizing such an amazing birthday in Paris that  was truly special.  Even  though  I  was  in  the  US,  I  completely  trusted  your  taste  and  your recommendations, and I am so glad I did!  When my guests and I walked in the  museum we were in total awe. Your prompt answers to my phone calls and emails and enthusiastic spirit made this weekend event EXCEPTIONAL. The private visits to ateliers that you arranged were such a fun experience!\r\nYou attention to detail such as sending a trendy guide book about Paris and a book of the museum Jacquemart-André  the  venue  where  we  had  the  event  to  our  guest  prior  the  birthday  weekend were greatly appreciated. The instant portrait you organized during the dinner by a renowned artist is hanging in my office. I rave about you to all my friends. »\r\nThe whole weekend was filled with surprises for the visits to ateliers, museums that you arranged were such a fun life long exprience! If you ever want a recommendation you can have them contact me directly!\r\n\" Alejandra Poupel is the ultimate Paris insider\"'),
	(9161,401,'_testimonials_2_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(9162,401,'testimonials_2_testimonial_name','Diana Morrison (USA)'),
	(9163,401,'_testimonials_2_testimonial_name','field_56e2c581ae172'),
	(9164,401,'testimonials_2_event_category','1'),
	(9165,401,'_testimonials_2_event_category','field_570d46e5dfd99'),
	(9166,401,'testimonials_3_testimonial_image','398'),
	(9167,401,'_testimonials_3_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(9168,401,'testimonials_3_testimonial_content','« For events with distinction, look no further.  Alejandra  Events  organized my dream  wedding anniversary.  With attention to the finest details and working diligently alongside the caterer, florist, musician and more, the event was a complete success!  The venue was breathtaking and the VIP haute couture jewelry atelier she organized for my family was extraordinary.  I highly recommend  working  with  her  because  she  makes  you feel  comfortable  every  step  of the way  and  you  can  actually  enjoy  your  event!   I  will  never  host  another  event  without  her. My friends are still talking about it… ».'),
	(9169,401,'_testimonials_3_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(9170,401,'testimonials_3_testimonial_name','Olena et Sergej Artamonov (Russie)'),
	(9171,401,'_testimonials_3_testimonial_name','field_56e2c581ae172'),
