	(9295,407,'_testimonials_4_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(9296,407,'testimonials_4_testimonial_content','« I just wanted to say thanks for the perfect baby shower. Every detail was beautifully attended to and thought out.  The decorations were stunning, and the event went off without one problem. Thank you so much for planning the fabulous and fun event. The signature pink lemonade and the cake in the shape of a tummy were an absolute hit ».'),
	(9297,407,'_testimonials_4_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
