	(9643,409,'_testimonials_5_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(9644,409,'testimonials_5_testimonial_content','« We couldn’t have planned this party without the wonderful services of Alejandra. An event in Paris has always been a dream of  ours, but such a daunting task from so far away. Alejandra was a lifesaver, she is knowledgeable of the city, flexible, dependable, and detail oriented, making sure we  had thought of everything.  She made our dream party a reality.  Thanks Alejandra! We can’t wait for another special occasion for you to plan! »'),
	(9645,409,'_testimonials_5_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
