	(10899,435,'dna_content','[:en]Professional, polished and poised\r\nAlejandra Poupel Events provides a full range of event services to a savvy and discerning clientele. Alejandra and her seasoned team collaborate with their creative partners to create world-class events that are masterfully produced and distinctively designed.\r\n\r\nWe work with events of every size and approach each one with unrivaled passion, inventiveness and sophistication. \r\n\r\nAnd our clients get more than just a well-crafted event. We have insider access to arrange private visits to art collector’s homes, couture atelier and backstage experiences. \r\n\r\nProfessional: Expand your perception of what is possible (as a side quote)\r\nOur agency’s clients are refined and insist on hiring the best craftsman to listen to their dreams, respect their culture and then execute an exquisite event. \r\n\r\nAlejandra is a sharp negotiator who will manage your budget with care. She has strong relationships with trusted vendors and suppliers who want to work with her to create exceptional events, defined by grace and created with an impeccable attention to detail.\r\n\r\nAlejandra Poupel Events will help you curate the perfect, personal event. Every detail will be handled with precision and care. She and her team operate in many languages and cultures but it said that Alejandra’s native tongue is the language of determination.\r\n\r\nPolished: A successful event is like a work of art\r\nAlejandra Poupel Events believes that every celebration is a work of art. We will handle every detail of your event, from A-Z. Alejandra is a master at listening to clients, creating a partnership with them and then working together from concept to completion.\r\n\r\nOur philosophy is to provide truly honest and thoughtful direction to our clients while utilizing our collective knowledge and experience to design, plan and seamlessly orchestrate an event that will delight all five senses.\r\n\r\nPoised: Alejandra Poupel loves to surprise and delight!\r\nOur fearless team knows how to deliver that wow factor — whether it’s a destination wedding or an intimate dinner with friends, it will be memorable, elegant and flawless. \r\n\r\nThe word “no” is not in her vocabulary, which is why clients rave about her. (link to References page) \r\n\r\nWhat truly differentiates us in the competitive landscape is our five-senses approach to creating spectacular and unique events that will leave you suspended in a moment with the profound longing to relive that moment — again and again. We create events from a theatrical point of view, with a beginning, middle and end. We shape a tempo that keep clients in awe and surprised. We design an experience using the five senses — through a subtle yet powerful scent wafting through the room or just-right lighting that captures a mood or delightful music that stirs emotions.\r\n\r\nSchedule your consultation to discover why so many have trusted us with their most precious moments.\r\n[:fr]Audace, distinction et exigence sont les maîtres-mots d’Alejandra Poupel Events. L’agence produit et organise chaque événement qui lui est confié dans un esprit de recherche et d\'innovation, de créativité et d\'émotion.\r\nCe sont des moments d’exception, dans lesquels se retrouve une certaine idée du Luxe, qui brille par son authenticité et par sa quête d’excellence et de perfection. Nous en connaissons les usages et nous les réinterprétons sans cesse pour mettre en avant la singularité de nos clients.\r\n\r\nVéritable trend-setter, il ne s’agit pas de décoder les tendances actuelles mais d’établir un nouvel air du temps... Notre capacité à se projeter et à anticiper les futures tendances émergentes nous permet de concevoir des événements novateurs tout préservant un sens de l’esthétisme et du raffinement.\r\n\r\nDes propositions « clé en main », sur-mesure et initiées par une écoute attentive des besoins et des désirs de nos clients. Aucune limite ! Le « non » ne faisant pas partie de notre vocabulaire ! Nous oeuvrons en toute confidentialité, préservant l’intimité de nos clients et faisant preuve de sollicitude à leur égard.\r\n\r\nNous avons également à cœur de respecter les coutumes propres à chaque culture et de trouver l’harmonie parfaite entre tradition et réinterprétation moderne. Une richesse culturelle avec laquelle nous travaillons quotidiennement et qui vient nourrir notre réflexion.[:]'),
