	(11491,445,'alejandra_2_alejandra_description','[:en]Alejandra’s commitment to her clients knows no bounds; she gives 110% all the time. For every location she discovers, there comes new inspiration and perspective. It is her keen curiosity about the world and how aesthetic, cultures and hospitality intertwine that make all her events something to talk about.[:fr]Folies des grandeurs à la mesure de son imagination, raffinement à la Française, esprit avant-gardiste très audacieux, Alejandra et son enthousiasme contagieux donneront vie à vos rêves le temps d’un événement d’exception, dans une ambiance grand luxe et une atmosphère feutrée.\r\n[:]'),
