	(12055,459,'services_4_service_description','[:en]<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Extraordinary events begin with big ideas. We believe obstacles don’t exist. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Just imagine …</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">An anniversary celebration at the Jacquemart-André museum in Paris</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A surprise birthday at a beach house in Monte Carlo</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A private wine tasting in a renowned vineyard</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">An intimate dinner for 50 in a private palazzo overlooking Venice</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">If you have amazing ideas and want someone to bring them to life, look no further than Alejandra Poupel Events. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"></p>[:fr]<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Extraordinary events begin with big ideas. We believe obstacles don’t exist. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Just imagine …</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">An anniversary celebration at the Jacquemart-André museum in Paris</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A surprise birthday at a beach house in Monte Carlo</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A private wine tasting in a renowned vineyard</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">An intimate dinner for 50 in a private palazzo overlooking Venice</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">If you have amazing ideas and want someone to bring them to life, look no further than Alejandra Poupel Events. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>How does it work?</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Dream</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Alejandra and her fearless team will start with a simple conservation — tell us what you are dreaming about. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Dream bigger</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Then we’ll brainstorm together to figure out the story you want to tell your guests and this will bring your idea into focus. We’ll review floor plans, get inspired by beautiful images and image the un-imaginable. Our collaborative relationship with clients is what sets us apart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Bringing the dream to life</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Next we will leverage our long-standing relationships with people throughout Europe to create a one-of-a-kind celebration. This is the point where you get to relax and let Alejandra’s commitment to innovative design and her ability to transcend trends create an event that is perfect — for you.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Schedule your consultation to discover why so many have trusted us with their most precious moments.</span></p>[:]'),
