	(13302,489,'testimonials_2_testimonial_image','399'),
	(13303,489,'_testimonials_2_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(13304,489,'testimonials_2_testimonial_content',' Alejandra, I truly want to thank you for organizing such an amazing birthday in Paris that  was truly special.  Even  though  I  was  in  the  US,  I  completely  trusted  your  taste  and  your recommendations, and I am so glad I did!  When my guests and I walked in the  museum we were in total awe. Your prompt answers to my phone calls and emails and enthusiastic spirit made this weekend event EXCEPTIONAL. The private visits to ateliers that you arranged were such a fun experience!\r\nYou attention to detail such as sending a trendy guide book about Paris and a book of the museum Jacquemart-André  the  venue  where  we  had  the  event  to  our  guest  prior  the  birthday  weekend were greatly appreciated. The instant portrait you organized during the dinner by a renowned artist is hanging in my office. I rave about you to all my friends.  Alejandra Poupel is the ultimate Paris insider\"'),
	(13305,489,'_testimonials_2_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(13306,489,'testimonials_2_testimonial_name','Diana Morrison (USA)'),
