	(13311,489,'_testimonials_3_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(13312,489,'testimonials_3_testimonial_content','« For events with distinction, look no further.  Alejandra  Events  organized my dream  wedding anniversary.  With attention to the finest details and working diligently alongside the caterer, florist, musician and more, the event was a complete success!  The venue was breathtaking and the VIP haute couture jewelry atelier she organized for my family was extraordinary.  I highly recommend  working  with  her  because  she  makes  you feel  comfortable  every  step  of the way  and  you  can  actually  enjoy  your  event!   I  will  never  host  another  event  without  her. My friends are still talking about it… ».'),
	(13313,489,'_testimonials_3_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(13314,489,'testimonials_3_testimonial_name','Olena et Sergej Artamonov (Russie)'),
