	(13334,489,'testimonials_6_testimonial_image','403'),
	(13335,489,'_testimonials_6_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(13336,489,'testimonials_6_testimonial_content','« Alejandra!  Our wedding planner extraordinaire!  How do we even begin? From the beginning you have been nothing but supportive, excited and generous as ever to us. I can’t even begin to tell  you  how  much  your  help  has  made  this  wedding  what  it  is.  Ever ything  from  vendor suggestions, creative ideas, to helping me create the perfect tempo and timeline for the party were amazing. Your care, your excitement and your vision exceeded our expectations. You told us what to  expect,  what  to  plan  for,  things  to  avoid  and  these  details  will  be  what  makes  the  day  so memorable. We are so excited to be married and  we just can’t thank you enough for making it happen. »'),
	(13337,489,'_testimonials_6_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(13338,489,'testimonials_6_testimonial_name','Hélène & Richard (France)'),
	(13339,489,'_testimonials_6_testimonial_name','field_56e2c581ae172'),
	(13340,489,'testimonials_6_event_category','4'),
	(13341,489,'_testimonials_6_event_category','field_570d46e5dfd99'),
	(13342,489,'testimonials_7_testimonial_image','404'),
	(13343,489,'_testimonials_7_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(13344,489,'testimonials_7_testimonial_content','« True  grace under fire!  There aren’t enough good things to say about Alejandra Poupel and the services  her  team  provided  for  our  wedding.  Being  thousands  of  miles  away,  we  were  able  to utilize  her  knowledge  and  expertise  to  plan  our  dream  destination  wedding  in  Paris,  the  most romantic  city  in  the  world,  with  no  stress  or  concerns.  The  special  attention  you  gave  my grandparents by helping them  enjoy  their  stay  to  the  fullest  for  our big day made the evening so incredibly special. The decorations were beyond  incredible, every detail was planned perfectly and we were able to be guest at our own wedding. »'),
	(13345,489,'_testimonials_7_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(13346,489,'testimonials_7_testimonial_name','Aito & Kanami (Japon)'),
	(13347,489,'_testimonials_7_testimonial_name','field_56e2c581ae172'),
