	(13709,493,'testimonials_5_testimonial_content','« Alejandra!  Our wedding planner extraordinaire!  How do we even begin? From the beginning you have been nothing but supportive, excited and generous as ever to us. I can’t even begin to tell  you  how  much  your  help  has  made  this  wedding  what  it  is.  Ever ything  from  vendor suggestions, creative ideas, to helping me create the perfect tempo and timeline for the party were amazing. Your care, your excitement and your vision exceeded our expectations. You told us what to  expect,  what  to  plan  for,  things  to  avoid  and  these  details  will  be  what  makes  the  day  so memorable. We are so excited to be married and  we just can’t thank you enough for making it happen. »'),
