	(13725,493,'testimonials_7_testimonial_content','« I feel like my wedding day wouldn’t have been as magical  without Alejandra and her team.  Even though  there  was a great number of guests  they  were  all  treated  as  if  we  were  having  an  intimate wedding. One of my highlights was our days together searching for the perfect wedding dress. The extravagant  and  lavish  experience  you  gave  us  was  beyond  expectations.  You  will  not  regret hiring Alejandra and her staff, well worth the investment! ».'),
