	(14842,503,'testimonials_4_testimonial_image','400'),
	(14843,503,'_testimonials_4_testimonial_image','field_56e2c559ae170'),
	(14844,503,'testimonials_4_testimonial_content','[:en]I just wanted to say thanks for the perfect baby shower. Every detail was beautifully attended to and thought out.  The decorations were stunning, and the event went off without one problem. Thank you so much for planning the fabulous and fun event. The signature pink lemonade and the cake in the shape of a tummy were an absolute hit[:fr]Je tiens à te remercier infiniment d’avoir organisé le « baby shower » parfait. Tu as pris soin de tous les détails et tu as su adapter ma vision pour me créer un concept d’événement très original et splendide. Le cocktail avec du champagne et limonade rose, ainsi que les mariachis ont créé une ambiance festive et inoubliable[:]'),
	(14845,503,'_testimonials_4_testimonial_content','field_56e2c567ae171'),
	(14846,503,'testimonials_4_testimonial_name','Valeria Kelly (USA)'),
	(14847,503,'_testimonials_4_testimonial_name','field_56e2c581ae172'),
