	(18153,644,'_services_title','field_56dc73ace2fe2'),
	(18154,644,'services_introduction','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>How does it work?</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Dream</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Alejandra and her fearless team will start with a simple conservation — tell us what you are dreaming about. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Dream bigger</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Then we’ll brainstorm together to figure out the story you want to tell your guests and this will bring your idea into focus. We’ll review floor plans, get inspired by beautiful images and image the un-imaginable. Our collaborative relationship with clients is what sets us apart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>Bringing the dream to life</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Next we will leverage our long-standing relationships with people throughout Europe to create a one-of-a-kind celebration. This is the point where you get to relax and let Alejandra’s commitment to innovative design and her ability to transcend trends create an event that is perfect — for you.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Schedule your consultation to discover why so many have trusted us with their most precious moments.</span></p>'),
	(18155,644,'_services_introduction','field_5763141200578'),
	(18156,644,'services_0_service_title','[:en]Weddings[:fr]Mariages[:]'),
	(18157,644,'_services_0_service_title','field_57630e44fe222'),
	(18158,644,'services_0_service_description','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">We believe that your wedding should be perfect and reflect your dreams, taste and style.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>A beautifully orestrated wedding should feel special and seamless and leave the bride and groom glowing. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">That’s why we create a partnership with couples to really understand exactly what they want. Alejandra interviews her clients as much as they interview her and once they’ve decided on each other, she will do anything for them!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The best part is that you just get to dream about what you want and then it’s our privilege to make it a reality. Our exceptional team of experts watches over every last detail because we want each guest to feel like they are sitting at the best table.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Every detail, from A-Z, will be handled with care and precision. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Romantic proposals</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Beautiful bridal showers</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Festive rehearsal dinners</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Over-the-top weddings</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Exotic honeymoon packages</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Bountiful brunches</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Insider cultural activities</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Hotel logistics and transportation services</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Concierge services</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">There’s an artistry in wedding planning and Alejandra executes every wedding as if it were her own daughter’s — with attention, care and passion. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Schedule your consultation to discover why so many have trusted us with their most precious moments.</span></p>'),
	(18159,644,'_services_0_service_description','field_57630e4efe223'),
	(18160,644,'services_0_service_quote','[:en]« Your happily ever after begins now »[:fr]« La folie des grandeurs, mais dans un souci du détail »[:]'),
