	(18246,646,'services_1_service_description','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">There’s no event too big or small. No request too simple or extravagant. From elegant and chic to warm and whimsical, any destination event can happen with ease in the capable hands of Alejandra.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Put me in a grand Venetian<i> </i>palace or a private, serene home in Lac Come, a remote Caribbean island or a fabulous villa along the Amalfi coast and ask me to create. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">There’s no limit to what can we can make happen …</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A romantic proposal in Paris</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">An exclusive dinner party in Venice</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A festive family reunion at a castle in Europe</span></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">A bar mitzvah on an elegant yacht</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Clients from all over the world have worked with Alejandra Poupel Events to transform their wildest dreams into their most favorite moments. We will handle everything from travel arrangements and transportation to personalized web sites and unique visits.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">One of our greatest strengths lies in interpreting our client’s preferences, assessing the possibilities and then translating them into a well-planned and well-designed event. Our years of hands-on experience allow us to navigate the complicated landscape of producing destination events.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Schedule your consultation to discover why so many have trusted us with their most precious moments.</span></p>'),
